pages.text: $(#f00)/hata reload$() Reload all hata textures$(br)$(#f00)/maid_res reload$() Reload the maid resource pack. This command does not completely reload some resources. It is recommended to use the F3+T shortcut key.$(br)$(#f00)/draw_coupon reload$() Reload draw coupon.$(br)$(#f00)/spell_card reload$() Reload all spell card data.
$(#f00)/touhou_little_maid power$() Set player power value$(br)$(#f00)/touhou_little_maid maid_num$() Set player's maid num
